# ESLint Before Session End

Before completing a session that includes code changes, run ESLint to fix formatting and lint issues:

```bash
npx eslint src/path/to/file.ts --fix
npm run lint:eslint -- --fix
```

## When to Run

- After making edits to source files
- Before committing changes
- Before ending the conversation with code modifications

## Example

```bash
# Fix all src files
npm run lint:eslint -- --fix

# Or fix specific files
npx eslint src/path/to/file.ts --fix
```
